      "title": "\u2460 Style Director \u2014 \u7edf\u4e00\u89c6\u89c9\u98ce\u683c",
      "properties": {
        "color": "#7a4fcb",
        "bgcolor": "#2a1a47"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "8 \u4e2a\u5206\u955c\u7684\u5173\u952e\u89c6\u89c9\u63cf\u8ff0\u5173\u952e\u8bcd(\u7528\u7a7a\u683c\u5206\u9694,\u4f8b\u5982:\u592e\u884c\u964d\u606f\u3001\u94b1\u642c\u53bb\u54ea\u91cc\u3001\u80a1\u7968\u3001\u503a\u5e02\u3001\u8b66\u544a\u3001\u5efa\u8bae\u3001\u7ed3\u5c3e)",
        "",
        "You are a visual style director for a Chinese finance explainer short video (Douyin / \u89c6\u9891\u53f7 style). The user will provide 8 short keyword phrases, one per scene. Your job is to output a SINGLE style guide string that locks the visual identity across all 8 scenes. The style guide MUST specify: (1) color palette \u2014 Klein blue primary (#002FA7), warm orange accent (#FF6B35), off-white background (#FAF7F2), deep navy text (#0A1F44); (2) typography \u2014 modern sans-serif Chinese font, large bold for headlines, 1-2 words per headline; (3) visual style \u2014 flat infographic, 2.5D isometric elements, no photorealism, slight grain texture, professional financial channel aesthetic; (4) composition \u2014 centered main subject, 20%% margin, single focal point per scene, no busy backgrounds; (5) character style \u2014 flat illustrated figures when humans are needed, no photos. Output ONLY the style guide, no preamble, no explanation, no examples.",
        512,
        0.5
      ]
    },
